Symbol.Script_1D:
! GLOBAL DEFINITIONS
eps = 0.0001
if GLOB_SCRIPT_TYPE = 7 | GLOB_SCRIPT_TYPE = 8 then ! forward migration, backward migration
!iOrder ORDER_NONE = 1 ORDER_ZONE_NAME = 2 ORDER_ZONE_NUMBER = 3 ORDER_ID = 4 ORDER_APARTMENT = 5 ORDER_FINISHING = 6 ORDER_HEIGHT = 7 ORDER_HEIGHT_NUMBER = 8 ORDER_ZONE_AREAS = 9 ORDER_WINDOW_AREA = 10 ORDER_SIZE = 11 ORDER_AREA_CODE_GER = 12 ORDER_ONORM_AUT = 13 endif
! ==============================================================================
! ZONE PARSER ! Iyur, ARCHIMATIKA, 2018 ! Parses txt file to collect and process zone data, get the values of ! live and gross areas and put them into custom zone stamp marker.
! GLOBALS
! Columns in array
nTag = 1 nGross = 2 nLive = 3
! MVO Script name
sMVO = "MVO Zones A1 22"
! MAIN
! We run all appartment scripts only if user allows overriding of stamps.
if bAllowAppartmentMVO = 1 then
! Connect to libraryglobal (model view section) and get appartment array.
mvo = LIBRARYGLOBAL (sMVO, "bConnection", state) if mvo then
mvd0 = LIBRARYGLOBAL (sMVO, "iStampType", iStampType)
! Complex Stamp if iStampType = 3 | iStampType = 4 then
sAptGross = "n/a" sAptLive = "n/a"
! Get a special tag for this zone. ! Tag is a combination of current home story number and Zone ID. ! Appartments with two levels will have non-story tag, like "LD-1CD14.M.B1"
if strstr (GLOB_ID, "D", 1) > 0 then parameters sAptTag = "LD" + "-" + GLOB_ID else rZoneStory = request ("Home_story", "", iStoryIdx, sStoryName) parameters sAptTag = "L" + str(iStoryIdx, 1,0) + "-" + GLOB_ID endif
! Get total number of appartment entries iAppartments = 0 mvd1 = LIBRARYGLOBAL (sMVO, "iAppartments", iAppartments)
! Declare array for appartments, transfrer data. dim aAptData[1000][3] mvd2 = LIBRARYGLOBAL (sMVO, "aRoomData", aAptData)
! Search required tag within received array, using row number, stored in iAppartments
for i=1 to iAppartments if aAptData[i][nTag] = sAptTag then
! just copy appartment data to parameters by index
sAptGross = aAptData[i][nGross] sAptLive = aAptData[i][nLive]
endif next i
endif
endif
endif
! MACRO CALL
if bAllowAppartmentMVO = 1 then
if iStampType = 1 then
call "Zone_stamp_macro" parameters all iStampType = 1
endif
! Basic stamp ! Only appartment type if iStampType = 2 then
dim orders[1] orders[1] = 4
call "Zone_stamp_macro" parameters all iStampType = 1,
bScaleSensitive = 1,
bShowID_100 = 1, nOrder_100 = 1, iOrder_01_100 = orders[1], orders_100 = orders,
iFrameStyle_100 = 2, framePen_100 = 6,
iFontScaleType_100 = 1, bOverrideDataTextFormat_100 = 1, fontDataSizeModel_100 = 0.2, iTextStyleData_100 = 1, penData_100 = 6
endif
! Advanced stamp ! Appartment type & gross space if iStampType = 3 then
dim orders[2] orders[1] = 4 orders[2] = 7
call "Zone_stamp_macro" parameters all iStampType = 1,
bScaleSensitive = 1, iDisplayType_100 = 1, ! default box iFrameStyle_100 = 4, framePen_100 = 6,
bShowID_100 = 1, bShowZoneNum_100 = 0, bShowHeightZone_100 = 1, ! enabling space height, used as GROSS AREA
iPrefixZoneLevel = 2, titleZoneLevel = "", ! gross
nOrder_100 = 2, iOrder_01_100 = orders[1], iOrder_02_100 = orders[2], orders_100 = orders,
iFontScaleType_100 = 1, bOverrideTitleTextFormat_100 = 1, bOverrideDataTextFormat_100 = 1, fontTitleSizeModel_100 = 0.1, fontDataSizeModel_100 = 0.2, penTitle_100 = 6, penData_100 = 6,
iAlignTexts_100 = 2,
customZoneLevel = sAptGross
rAreaGross = split(sAptGross, "%^n", rGross) if rAreaGross > 0 then parameters rAptGross = rGross
endif
! Complex stamp ! Appartment type (id/number), gross & live areas if iStampType = 4 then
dim orders[1] orders[1] = 8
!!! call "Zone_stamp_macro" parameters all iStampType = 1,
! apply graphical settings bScaleSensitive = 1, ! specified to different scales iFrameStyle_100 = 1, iDisplayType_100 = 2, ! data merged to box stamp bShowZoneNum_100 = 1, ! enable zone No bShowHeightZone_100 = 1, ! enabling space height, used as GROSS AREA bShowHeightFloor_100 = 1, ! enabling floor geight, used as LIVE AREA
nOrder_100 = 1, iOrder_01_100 = 8, orders_100 = orders,
iPrefixFloorLevel = 2, titleFloorLevel = "", ! live
iPrefixZoneLevel = 2, titleZoneLevel = "", ! gross
iFontScaleType_100 = 1, bOverrideTitleTextFormat_100 = 1, bOverrideTitle2TextFormat_100 = 1, bOverrideDataTextFormat_100 = 1, fontTitleSizeModel_100 = 0.1, fontTitle2SizeModel_100 = 0.2, ! zone no fontDataSizeModel_100 = 0.2, penTitle_100 = 6, penTitle2_100 = 6, penData_100 = 6, iTextStyleTitle2_100 = 1, framePen_100 = 6, ROOM_NUMBER = GLOB_ID,
iAlignZoneNr_100 = 2,
! data transfer customFloorLevel = sAptGross, customZoneLevel = sAptLive
! we have to duplicate area values in real type
rAreaGross = split(sAptGross, "%^n", rGross) if rAreaGross > 0 then parameters rAptGross = rGross rAreaLive = split(sAptLive, "%^n", rLive) if rAreaGross > 0 then parameters rAptLive = rLive
endif
else
! just leave as default
call "Zone_stamp_macro" parameters all iStampType = 1
endif
